            "heading": "",
            "text": "<h6>Exploring Designs</h6><p>It’s time to delve into your wedding ring design details! You can view our existing rings in person, online, or via the online builder. Once your stone and setting details are decided, we will start sourcing your unique gemstones!</p>",
